Merge pull request #341 from emansih/master Fix  java.lang.IllegalStateException

Fix java.lang.IllegalStateException ` java.lang.IllegalStateException: You can't start or clear loads in RequestListener or Target callbacks. If you must do so, consider posting your into() or clear() calls to the main thread using a Handler instead.` is thrown on Glide 4.2.0 onwards.  To fix this issue see https://github.com/bumptech/glide/issues/2473
